<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَلَمْ تُجَاوِزْ قَدْرَ الحَاجَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَإِنْ جَاوَزَتْهُ، أَوْ كَانَ وَضَعَهَا عَلَى غَيْرِ طَهَارَةٍ؛ وَجَبَ نَزْعُهَا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- فَإِنْ خَافَ ضَرَرًا؛ تَيَمَّمَ مَعَ مَسْحِ مَوْضُوعَةٍ عَلَى طَهَارَةٍ مُجَاوِزَةٍ مَحَلَّ الحَاجَةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> إِنْ ظَهَرَ بَعْضُ مَحَلِّ فَرْضٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> أَوْ حَصَلَ مَا يُوجِبُ الغُسْلَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> أَوِ انْقَضَتِ المُدَّةُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>بَطَلَ الوُضُوءُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> نَوَاقِضُ الوُضُوءِ ثَمَانِيَةٌ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> خَارِجٌ مِنْ سَبِيلٍ مُطْلَقًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَخُرُوجُ:<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- بَوْلٍ أَوْ غَائِطٍ مِنْ بَاقِي البَدَنِ، قَلَّ أَوْ كَثُرَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- أَوْ غَيْرِهِمَا؛ كَقَيْءٍ، أَوْ دَمٍ إِنْ فَحُشَ فِي نَفْسِ كُلِّ أَحَدٍ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>